    "slug": "coconut-shell-granular-activated-carbon",
    "status": "publish",
    "type": "product",
    "link": "https://file.goldcarbon.net/product/coconut-shell-granular-activated-carbon/",
    "title": {
      "rendered": "Coconut Shell Granular Activated Carbon"
    },
    "content": {
      "rendered": "\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Product Overview</h2>\n\n\n\n<p class=\"is-style-default\">Coconut shell granular activated carbon is manufactured from high-quality coconut shells through carbonization and activation processes. It features a highly developed microporous structure, exceptional hardness, and superior adsorption performance.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Specifications</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-table\"><table class=\"has-fixed-layout\"><tbody><tr><td>Iodine Number</td><td>900-1100 mg/g</td></tr><tr><td>Particle Size</td><td>4&#215;8, 6&#215;12, 8&#215;16, 12&#215;40 mesh</td></tr><tr><td>Moisture</td><td>≤5%</td></tr><tr><td>Ash Content</td><td>≤8%</td></tr><tr><td>Hardness</td><td>≥95%</td></tr><tr><td>Bulk Density</td><td>0.45-0.55 g/cm³</td></tr></tbody></table></figure>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Applications</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul class=\"wp-block-list\">\n<li>Drinking water treatment and purification</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Industrial wastewater treatment</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Air purification and odor removal</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Gold recovery in mining operations</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Food and beverage processing</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Pharmaceutical purification</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Packaging</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Standard packaging: 25kg/bag, 500kg/ton bag<br>Custom packaging available upon request<br>Storage: Keep in dry place, avoid moisture and direct sunlight</p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"1024\" height=\"572\" src=\"/images/products/coconut-shell-granular-activated-carbon-content-1775097108830.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-21\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></figure>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
    "excerpt": {
      "rendered": "<p>Product Overview Coconut shell granular activated carbo [&hellip;]</p>\n",
      "protected": false
    },
